Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:07.34,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつか君と見上げた空は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:19.00,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心の中　そっと溶けていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:31.35,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}白いノートに書いた手紙は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:43.19,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}行く先を告げないまま閉じ込めた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:53.98,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}言葉にすれば戻れないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:08.64,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつも君と見上げた空は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:24.29,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}悲しいくらい青く  透きとおっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:07.34,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}曾几何时与你一起仰望过的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:19.00,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}渐渐溶入了心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:31.35,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}白色的笔记本上写的信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:43.19,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}还未说明用意就匆匆合上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:53.98,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}因为话语总是覆水难收
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:08.64,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}总与你一同仰望的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:24.29,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}蔚蓝清澈得令人悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:22:02.18,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}スローモーション　蘇る校舎の影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:10.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕陽を浴びながら　私たちは笑ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:21.25,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}お互いあの時から変わってない身長なんだけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:28.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見える景色　変わったかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:32.35,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じポケットじゃないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:36.60,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ宝物が眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:40.95,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喜び悲しみ全部share!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:45.56,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}分け合って泣いて笑ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:54.23,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一緒だよ　違った道の上でも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:22:02.18,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}慢镜回放校舍的影子中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:10.00,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沐浴着夕阳的我们在欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:21.25,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们从那时起虽然身高都没变化
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:28.00,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可是看到的风景却变了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:32.35,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然各自拥有不同的口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:36.60,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可里边却睡着同样的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:40.95,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欢乐和悲伤全都share!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:45.56,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}分享着我们的眼泪与笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:54.23,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永远在一起  就算走在不同的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立 敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 不要在走廊里跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭啦～吃饭啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太快啦 小清
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:02:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯 哎呀 已经到午饭时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 一起去吃便当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...为什么女孩子之间不能相爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间同学...你刚才说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊 旧病又复发了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好失礼啊 我的想法从来没变过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没变过? 女孩子之间?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子以外的人我从来没喜欢过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对对 你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要光你们两个聊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子啊 是喜欢女孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么稀奇的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你考女高不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去考了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能考得上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在面试时候被问到报考理由...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是说...比如我这样的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 我喜欢的是可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这次是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...这本书有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...那我查一下就叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请八号还书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 前辈?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是开书店的 说非常感谢太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奇怪 一点都不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有什么想吃的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.35,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(章鱼先生是用维也纳香肠做的然后油炸成章鱼的样子\N一般小孩子的便当里才会出现)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.90,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}(<風立ちぬ>是堀辰雄在二十世纪三十年代\N陆续发表的一部小说据说是新心理主义文学的代表作...)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是要命啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼...啊这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:08:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是开书店的 说非常感谢太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她总是这样哦 很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要保密的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始只是觉得她写的字真好看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过回过神来 发现她的手和手指都非常美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过举手投足形容言语都非常有女孩子味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么可爱又那么漂亮 简直是犯规呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀...我倒是不明白...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她身边就觉得很温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的兴趣是读书和制作点心...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有男朋友的吧 既然那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有什么男朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是男朋友 也许有喜欢的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你肯定又是作茧自缚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从初中开始你一直都这样的啊 风间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一个人胡思乱想 自己一个人热情高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后肯定都被拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是别再这样了? 纯粹浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是这样呢 风间同学这样的美女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要男朋友的话 要多少都...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想高高兴兴吃顿饭的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 请二十一号还书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真是的 我又说非常感谢了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈有喜欢的男孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没有的啊那种男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我对前辈...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的吗 我也一直喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立 敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了让你们不要跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长 副班长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们帮忙准备一下世界史的教材 阿部老师说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学在和风间同学闹别扭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:11:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们今天都没有说话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨同学真是个好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了 一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还去上次去的那个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因为风间还在图书室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点和好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小清 要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想午饭总那么难吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友...真的很好啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜托你锁门了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那边已经结束了 我帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 风间同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同学里有一个男孩子喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我不小心又说了非常感谢的那个男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他...一直...都是为了风间同学才到图书室来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 他还问我能不能帮他问问你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你有没有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间 完了没?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯...前辈她...前辈她...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么嘛 风间一点都没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是前辈...非常生气地瞪着我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她凭什么对你生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个傻女人啊 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再为那种家伙哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说前辈是那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有什么舍不得吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...刚才还非常喜欢的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...不管是谁...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不想看到喜欢的人哭的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我这么个奇怪的朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怪 又傻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯 永远都做我的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 真没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远都要这样单相思下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:20:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望我喜欢的人也喜欢我而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 只是这样...而已呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 风间同学 你的维也纳香肠好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢 谢谢~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经...和好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:20:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是小纯先开口的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得看看你的反应应该会很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好玩?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再给你个 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分 不过我要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起什么事而笑我倒是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起什么事而哭?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是昨天看的电影啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.89,0:23:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对昨天的还礼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大家好 我是朱宫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.58,0:23:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上来就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是这和原作一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也无所谓 下一话是讲什么的来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.05,0:23:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.39,0:23:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下周再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:51.79,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}下一话 可爱的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

